      "title": "CWC to support Ranil at today\u2019s election",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "After much deliberation, the Ceylon Workers' Congress (CWC) has decided to support Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe in his bid for the Presidency, MP Jeevan Thondaman said today.",
        "Posting a message on his official Twitter, he extended his wishes to Dullas Alahapperuma and Anura Kumara Dissanayake as well. (CS)"
      ],
